title: Piece of World Trade Center
author: Unknown
pages:
This Piece of World
Trade Center Steel
Was Presented to
Gander International
Airport by the
Stephen Siller Tunnel
to Towers Foundation
on September 11,
2016,
In Gratitude for the
Profound Humanitarian
Role the Airport and
People of Gander
Played in The Wake of

the Attacks on 9/11.

Displayed in Gander
International Airport,
Gander, Newfoundland,
Newfoundland and
Labrador
